{"tid":2257512,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–壓力時候體溫會升高","createTime":"2020-10-25T08:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T01:41:55.000Z","uid":38861,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fbea30cfa0c5e50d3646707353244e8050aee0aa","tid":2257512,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:16:59.000Z","msg":"壓力大的時候，周不時體溫會升高，究竟是甚麼原因引致而成?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X2OrN4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X2OrN4.jpg&h=c6719f43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n科學家利用老鼠作研究對象，並提出圖中所示的理論（Ref1)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEtBAGs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEtBAGs.jpg&h=3c7d2c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大腦各部份接收得到壓力訊息後，利用神經線作訊息傳遞媒體，透過DP/DTT及rmR區域，最終誘使啡色脂肪產生熬能，引致體溫升高的現象。<br />\n<br />\n想對啡色脂肪作進一步了解的話，可閱覽之前所寫下的文章：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/473954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F473954&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=f7309a8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/473954</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手掌寫3個大字能減緩壓力這個廣泛流傳的理論，很有可能潛移默化地影響MD區域，從而能夠減輕壓力所產生的現象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5m0hUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5m0hUR.jpg&h=513a339c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦即是某程度來說，只要我們的認知認為見工、公眾演說、才藝表現等事件並不會引起壓力的話，的確是可以減輕部份壓力所引發的現象。<br />\n<br />\n之於可否利用藥物來透過短暫抑制上述機制來減輕壓力，理論上及實際上亦不是短期間可實踐的事，倒不如透過意志及積累經驗來抑制壓力引致的不良反應還來得實際。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=efade157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=aba9a02e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=49e2ee00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/367/6482/1105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F367%2F6482%2F1105&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=dd84beef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/367/6482/1105</a>"},{"pid":"aef772578e998a5a7d5be3a51a4a5f8089281190","tid":2257512,"uid":155238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"咁鬼佬寫咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468fd65b3ef193fc31415ca453c5518f896467d8","tid":2257512,"uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":