":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:16:34.000Z","msg":"扑嘢時身體都好熱，應該都係壓力大<br />\n<br />\n見工時，壓力大但唔會急屎，但之後個肚會有好多不需要的&ldquo;風&rdquo;，然後係咁放屁"},{"pid":"f3ecd83a9e0d0b9359e56ed180c007b7264bff83","tid":2257512,"uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YFkG0qWjsfU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYFkG0qWjsfU&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=63992a91\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YFkG0qWjsfU</a><br />\n靜觀減額課程&mdash;&mdash;資深臨床心理學家馬淑華博士"},{"pid":"374cdeb7b0f67f244430d3ed7e6139dd617bc8c6","tid":2257512,"uid":381265,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"使咩咁複雜，中學都有教過 gas law<br />\nPV=nRT, 其中 P 係壓力，T係温度<br />\nP 上升，其他volume 同 number of particle 不變，T 咪上升囉<br />\n<br />\n多謝 physics 呀 sir"},{"pid":"5767a00ec31c016d60a02d3adb3d6698a2328077","tid":2257512,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"374cdeb7b0f67f244430d3ed7e6139dd617bc8c6","tid":2257512,"uid":381265,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"使咩咁複雜，中學都有教過 gas law<br />\nPV=nRT, 其中 P 係壓力，T係温度<br />\nP 上升，其他volume 同 number of particle 不變，T 咪上升囉<br />\n<br />\n多謝 physics 呀 sir"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"如果真係要咁樣亂「玩」，壓力時候血管的體積都會有改變，V唔係constant。"},{"pid":"a181eddbc313af4561be75d1c1f1f2ea2e9b6920","tid":2257512,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5767a00ec31c016d60a02d3adb3d6698a2328077","tid":2257512,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"374cdeb7b0f67f244430d3ed7e6139dd617bc8c6","tid":2257512,"uid":381265,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"使咩咁複雜，中學都有教過 gas law<br />\nPV=nRT, 其中 P 係壓力，T係温度<br />\nP 上升，其他volume 同 number of particle 不變，T 咪上升囉<br />\n<br />\n多謝 physics 呀 sir"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T09:36:45.0